data.description: Situated in the desirable Arrowhead Lakes neighborhood of Willis, Texas, this adorable home is the perfect place to call home. With a private lake and pool, the neighborhood is the ideal spot to relax and enjoy the outdoors. The home itself is spacious and well-appointed, with an open-concept floor plan that is perfect for entertaining. Granite countertops and tile on the main floor add to the luxurious feel of the home. The spacious backyard has plenty of room for a pool, patio, or garden. This move-in ready home won't last long, so call today to schedule a showing!
